name: com.castsoftware.jaxws
title: JAX-WS Analyzer
description: This extension provides support for JAX-WS Web Services used in JEE applications. It handles a collection of annotations introduced with JAX-WS 2.0 (JSR 224) enabling the definition of SOAP Web Service contracts directly inside the java code. This extension also detects Web Service implementations when Apache CXF/Spring framework is used (through XML configuration files) and client-side Web Services created via Spring WebServiceTemplate.
